r"> <div class="waved-container"> <div class="green-wave"></div> <div class="light-wave"></div> <div class="waved-container-content"> <div class="wrapper"> <h3>Other diseases in this section</h3> <ul class="related-list"> <li class="related-item"> <a class="related-item__link" href="hronicheskaya-obstruktivnaya-bolezn-legkih.html"> <h5 class="related-item__title">Chronic obstructive pulmonary disease</h5> <p class="related-item__text">A slowly progressive disease associated with airflow limitation and chronic inflammation of the airways and lung tissue.</p> </a> </li> <li class="related-item"> <a class="related-item__link" href="ostrye-respiratornye-zabolevaniya.html"> <h5 class="related-item__title">Acute respiratory diseases</h5> <p class="related-item__text">A group of infectious diseases of a viral, bacterial, less often other nature, with a primary lesion of the upper respiratory tract and bronchi.</p> </a> </li> <li class="related-item"> <a class="related-item__link" href="bronhialnaya-astma.html"> <h5 class="related-item__title">Bronchial asthma</h5> <p class="related-item__text">Chronic inflammatory disease of the airways leading to bronchial obstruction.</p> </a> </li> </ul> </div> </div> </div> </div> <hzy-kb-menu-toggle></hzy-kb-menu-toggle>



        


